{"tid":1418059,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[物資檢討]真心full gear企後面要屌","createTime":"2019-08-05T17:45:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T06:42:53.000Z","uid":82920,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"e43ff957f87bef5a5644961f744648b86dce6257","tid":1418059,"uid":82920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:45:49.000Z","msg":"今日遍地開花<br />\n我唔知其他地方咩境<br />\n但我眼見，好多人full gear坐係度㩒手機<br />\n前線要gear個時幫手嗌<br />\n但又唔除自己個d出去<br />\n我唔理你係咪自己買<br />\n前面瘋狂食彈無頭盔無雙罐，你就有齊坐後面<br />\n後面物資站無晒比5到出去<br />\n<br />\n仲有人鏈問題<br />\n無衝突時人鏈係有效<br />\n但前線博擊個陣，仲企到勁密人鏈其實慢過行路拎過去<br />\n <br />\n我唔知下次衝突點<br />\n但我覺得需要起個戰線崗位post(好似之前有人整過)<br />\n但要詳細版<br />\n<br />\n例如:<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;-前線&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;-<br />\n消防員篇:射水兵，水桶兵，反擲兵<br />\n守線人士:遮組牆，鐵馬組<br />\n進攻:磚撚，遮撚，裝備撚<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;中線&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;-<br />\n目的:保護前線<br />\n保護篇:群兵(散企)，睇水兵(gup狗加指揮前中線)，物資兵，補水兵(斟水比前線射)，十字人(first aid)<br />\n<br />\n物資篇:駐守team，收集team，中轉站速遞，<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">前線速遞</span></span>，製gear team(磚，棍，etc)<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;後線&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n目的:見到乜新聞live消息即放上tg同社交平台<br />\n文宣，tg發言人，補gear<br />\n<br />\n我知我好應該好多甩溜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 亦好唔詳細，但我覺得需要文宣一下大家可以點做，而唔係坐係度打卡感受氣氛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為見住前線tun返黎，乜gear都無。。。<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de7ff823b0fb849cfa9cb58687facbacaf7c8377","tid":1418059,"uid":190847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T04:39:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a062faae794676bbaf92267d0fe71d8d0e07753","tid":1418059,"uid":190847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T06:38:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5321e329746706e484fdd81389f66eecb